@startuml
[*] --> PowerOnCheck
PowerOnCheck --> Problem : startup failure
PowerOnCheck --> Ready : startup successful

Ready --> Reset : reset
Ready --> Activate : activate
Ready --> Off : turn off

Activate --> Monitoring : activation successful

Monitoring --> Alarm : sensor triggered
Alarm --> Monitoring : false alarm or time ends
Alarm --> Ready : password entered

Monitoring --> Ready : password entered

Reset --> Ready : reset successful
Off --> Ready : power off
@enduml
